{
  "id": "adv_main_02_01_05",
  "title": "東京編1章5話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、不安なんですよね？\n本当は……逃げ出したいぐらい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you’re worried‚ aren’t you?\nThe truth is… you’re so worried you want to run away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、盗み聞きするつもりは\nなかったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Forgive us. We didn’t mean to\neavesdrop on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの声\n入り口のすぐ外にまで聞こえてきて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we heard your voice‚ {user}-san‚\njust outside your door.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.466666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうか独り言聞かれたのか。でも、二人が\n気にすることじゃない。ポロッと愚痴っちゃっただけで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… I see. So you heard me talking to myself. But you both\nshouldn’t worry about it. I was just venting a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.446652710743443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ウソ\n{user}さん、また強がってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Liar.\n{user}-san‚ you’re just pretending to be strong again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.079986044076776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんがいなくなってからの様子をずっと\n見ていれば、私達にだってなんとなく分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just watching your behavior ever since Saegusa-san left\nhas made it pretty clear to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.04665271074344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……はは\n隠せてたつもりなんだけどな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha…\nI thought I managed to hide it from you guys…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.90322858125736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "隠せる訳、ないじゃないですか\nだって{user}さんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How could you possibly hide it from us?\nCome on‚ {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.96989524792402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の近くにずっといてくれている\nマネージャーなんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you’re always by our side.\nYou’re our manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.26989524792403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そう。それにただ近くにいるだけの関係じゃないんです\n少しぐらいは、理解しているつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. And you’re more than just someone who’s by our side.\nSo I like to think we understand you‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8365619145907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私達をここまで導いてくれて\nその喜びを、一緒に分かち合ってくれる人のことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve led us this far‚\nand you’ve shared our joys with us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.10322858125736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 66.13656191459067
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 66.13656191459067
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 66.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "……必ず頂点に立って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I promised myself I’d stand at the top",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんを\nトップアイドルのマネージャーにしなきゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and make you\nthe manager of a top idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.06989524792401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 74.56989524792401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_19_05-mna016.m4a",
      "text": "それが私の本当の夢",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was my true dream.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.56989524792401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 78.60322858125735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈が叶えたかった、本当の夢）\n（叶えることが出来ない、本当の夢）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana’s true dream. The dream she wanted to actualize.）\n（The true dream she wasn’t able to actualize herself.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.90322858125734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（だが麻奈は、夢は叶ったと言って消えた）\n（二人が必ずトップアイドルになると確信出来たから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But as she disappeared‚ Mana said her dream did come true.）\n（That was because she was sure you two would become top idols.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.53656191459069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈は、託して消えたんだ。自分の夢をさくらや）\n（琴乃達に……なら、俺がやるべきことは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana disappeared‚ entrusting her dream to Sakura）\n（and Kotono‚ and the others… That means my duty now is to…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.73656191459072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.30322858125736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……そうだな、ごめん\n確かに、一人で抱え込んでいたのかもしれない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… You’re right. Sorry.\nI guess I was keeping all of my struggles to myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.28143723438951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですよ、そんなの\n{user}さんには前科があるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You shouldn’t do that.\nYou already have a prior record of similar crimes‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.31477056772287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はは……\n他にも言い方があるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha…\nI’m sure there’s a better way to phrase that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.94810390105626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも前に、そのせいで倒れたのは事実ですよね\nもっと私達のこと、信頼して話して下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you can’t deny that you fainted from stress a while ago.\nYou need to trust us and tell us more about your problems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.31477056772296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。でも、もう大丈夫。おかげで決心がついたから\n心配かけてごめん。それと……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. But I’m okay now. You helped me arrive at a decision.\nSorry I worried you. And also… thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.91477056772317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "あっ……えへへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Hee hee…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3744367488883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どういたしまして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’re welcome.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.20926679458836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと～さくら？　琴乃？\n何していますの？　遅過ぎますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! Sakura? Kotono?\nWhat is the reason for your prolonged delay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.72298571752145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、そうだった！　私達\n{user}さんを呼びに来たんだった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! That’s right! We were\nsupposed to fetch you‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7563190508549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_05-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "これから{user}さんと、橋本さんを\n晩ご飯に誘おうと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were going to invite you and Hashimoto-san\nout to dinner with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.25631905085493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
